narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Much the skills that one would expect; reading competency at a very basic level in French.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This class made me skeptical of the 1-semester "X-Language For Reading" course model, as dramatic sacrifices in terms of depth of knowledge seemed necessary to accommodate any measurable amount of progress. That being said, with the very high watermark of proficiency this class tried to establish with limited time and resources, it was executed very well.
